## ⚠️ Remaining Feature Placeholders

To ensure the app runs without crashing, the following features are currently using placeholder implementations because they require external API keys/setup that are not yet available:

1.  **Push Notifications**:
    - [src/services/pushNotification.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/mobile/src/services/pushNotification.ts) is safe-guarded to run without Firebase.
    - Status: Logs "Firebase not configured yet" warning.

2.  **Location Sharing**:
    - [LocationPickerScreen.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/mobile/src/screens/main/LocationPickerScreen.tsx) shows a placeholder UI instead of a map.
    - Status: Displays "Maps feature requires additional setup".

These are **not errors** but intentional placeholders until Firebase/Google Maps keys are provided.
